 ------------------
/ PROJECT LAYOUT /
-----------------

- build/
  Destination for all compiled Java classes.

- build.xml
  Used by Ant. 

- conf/
  Configuration directory.

- dist/
  - api/
    Destination for javadoc-generated documentation.
  - lib/
    Project .jar files.

- doc/
  - API
    API class and method summary.

- java/
  - lib/
      Third-party JAR files included with Grouper.
  - src/
      Grouper's Java source code.  
  - tests/
      Java source used for testing Grouper.

- LICENSE
  A copy of the Academic Free License v. 2.1

- README
    This file.

- sql/
    SQL commands for creating and populating the Groups registry
    database.


 --------------------------
/ BUILD AND INSTALLATION /
-------------------------

  % ant build
  % hsqldb-init.sh
  % ant test

To build the javadoc(1) documentation:
  % ant javadoc

